story: Al Asad airbase is operated by the United States Air Force. Some of its aircraft include the Boeing C-17 Globemaster III (transport aircraft), General Dynamics F-16 Fighting Falcon (aircraft fighter), and the Lockheed AC-130 which can be found on USAF aircraft carriers. The USAF was involved in the Invasion of Panama.
